item.description: 2020 年 7 月 1 日（星期三） 今日待办 编程 SIP BYE vs CANCEL For short, BYE is used when the callee already pick up the phone and talk for a while, otherwise, CANCEL takes place. 参考： Introduction to SIP BYE, CANCEL and hop-by-hop messages [video]understanding difference between sip bye & cancel request
